    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="553444671">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-553444671" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-553444671" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="553444671">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/iamsmoky/">[已注销]</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2013-11-25</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">这学期授课指定了这本书（英文原版）作教材，因为它比其他基本类似教科书便宜一点。之前大致翻了一下，感觉尚可。现在备课细读，后悔不已，里边一些观点实在不能认同，写得也不是特别有趣。还是巴比的那本书好一些，Adler和Clark的那本也很不错。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="314043703">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-314043703" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-314043703" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="314043703">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/dhzkaren/">喵巫</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2010-11-14</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">一本充满冷笑话的书，而译者是个天然呆！</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
